          "settings": {
            "title": "About IN 10 PRO",
            "default_open_1": "No",
            "title_1": "What is the top speed of the Yozma IN10 Pro?",
            "answer_1": "<p>The top speed reaches 75KM/H, delivering powerful acceleration for both urban commuting and short leisure rides.</p>",
            "default_open_2": "No",
            "title_2": "How many riding modes are available?",
            "answer_2": "<p>IN 10 Pro offers three speed modes (approx. 35KM/H, 55KM/H, 75KM/H) for different riding preferences.</p>",
            "default_open_3": "No",
            "title_3": "What rider height is the IN10 Pro suitable for?",
            "answer_3": "<p>The IN10 Pro is suitable for riders between 4.7 ft and 6.3 ft in height and is recommended for users aged 14 years and above.</p>",
            "default_open_4": "No",
            "title_4": "How long does it take to fully charge the battery?",
            "answer_4": "<p>With the 60V 5A US standard charger (XLR head), a full charge takes about 6–7 hours.</p>",
            "default_open_5": "No",
            "title_5": "What type of motor does it use?",
            "answer_5": "<p>IN 10 Pro features a 5000W mid-drive motor for superior power delivery and climbing ability compared to hub motors.</p>",
            "default_open_6": "No",
            "title_6": "What is the battery specification? Is it removable?",
            "answer_6": "<p>It comes with a 60V 27AH lithium battery that’s removable for convenient charging and maintenance.</p>",
            "default_open_7": "No",
            "title_7": "What is the max load capacity?",
            "answer_7": "<p>The maximum load is 150KG, suitable for most riders.</p>",
            "default_open_8": "No",
            "title_8": "How is the suspension system?",
            "answer_8": "<p>It features 45mm front and 48mm rear shock absorbers (black front, red rear) for enhanced stability on both urban and off-road terrain.</p>",
            "default_open_9": "No",
            "title_9": "How is the headlight performance at night?",
            "answer_9": "<p>It comes with dual-beam headlights (separate high/low beams) offering wider, brighter, and more energy-efficient illumination.</p>",
            "default_open_10": "No",
            "title_10": "What are the seat height and dimensions?",
            "answer_10": "<p>Seat height is 78CM, wheelbase 115CM, and overall size 168*70*105cm.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_F8KTND": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "title": "About IN 10",
            "default_open_1": "Yes",
            "title_1": "What‘s in the box?",
            "answer_1": "<p>Yozma E-bike*1<br/>48V 23.4Ah Lithium-Ion*1<br/>Battery Charger*1<br/>Assembly Tools*1<br/>Pedals*2<br/>Handle Bars Shipped Installed On Bike*1<br/>User Manual*1<br/>Number plate decals*1 <br/>Note: Please keep this box for at least 30 days in case of return or after-sales service.</p>",
