            "title_3": "The motorcycle has a short travel distance after charging. What's wrong?",
            "answer_3": "<p>1.Battery is not fully charged or battery life is declining.<br/>2.Tires may not be properly inflated.<br/>3.Frequent high-speed riding, uphill travel, heavy braking, or overloading can reduce range.</p>",
